{"tid":300941,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「王維基」高調「藐視」香港年青人，反映d咩？","createTime":"2017-06-28T09:50:42.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-01T01:37:15.000Z","uid":29314,"like":16,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"30a39353565f6585f0ff15422095165949c52e59","tid":300941,"uid":29314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-28T09:50:42.000Z","msg":"前人種樹，後人乘涼，香港剛好相反，上一代累積財富，下一代用畢生積蓄去繼續增長前人的財富。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n曾經是香港仔精神嘅王維基，最近都高調「藐視」香港年青人，都係老土的唔捱得，唔夠勤力，「因為未ready而去投訴社會唔畀機會，我唔係好贊成呢種態度。」<br />\n<br />\n這句說由他講出來相當諷刺，其實香港人同樣可以回敬佢「未ready就去投訴行會唔發個電視牌。」將制度不公平合理化，王維基好像忘記了，當初就是這班年青人最支持他搞電視台，其實最埋怨別人唔畀機會的，正是王維基本人，這讓我想起，另一位埋怨對手蝕錢但不肯執笠的傳媒地產商人。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n後記：傳媒寒冬，已經寒咗幾年，倒閉的同業已有數間，香港人睇新聞習慣已經改變，別說賺大錢，好新聞和收入，由正比變成反比，明星食煙偷食，好像比國家大事更為重要，&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;當我看到今年書展主題是「旅遊」，便知道傳媒就快玩完。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n要考量一個地方的文化軟實力，可以留意市民的閱讀普及程度和質素，今年書展以旅遊書作主題，港人願意花一百幾十買在Google可以免費找到的資訊，卻不肯每月花時間去支持新聞資訊，完全是為香港回歸廿年寫下悲歌。"},{"pid":"3a84e2419c40eda6014d53682264290de48d350c","tid":300941,"uid":56714,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-28T10:20:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b88326a0d7c605395ff06d62a998b1a4bbc09ca6","tid":300941,"uid":15711,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-28T10:21:38.000Z","msg":"咁都up 得出，王維基好失望<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，無面回帖<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"09f45c93cbbe9cf2285cc389f954e368dd43dd67","tid":300941,"uid":15984,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-28T10:23:49.000Z","msg":"連登仔係香港未來<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e7a3960f53dc4b0d8868b02b2533c4916822895","tid":300941,"uid":34001,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-28T10:35:35.000Z","msg":"始終都係生意佬一名"},{"pid":"e6c711294a2fffdeb50ccd0c06b8c9d39c86ad2c","tid":300941,"uid":29314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-28T17:29:23.000Z","msg":"好彩我從來都無吹奏過王維基"},{"pid":"2a2848dd8e9742139f0b6171d48c49774cd15b9c","tid":300941,"uid":5591,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-28T18:54:55.000Z","msg":"你係威過班廢青，但到頭來咪又係比隻六八狗當狗咁撚，巴乜撚野閉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a200666af526d55a7f1e443f0d309d2f983a89d","tid":300941,"uid":29314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-29T17:32:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a9437ca5a223f8b553801c49047e4d1bd8944f7","tid":300941,"uid":47558,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-29T17:37:07.000Z","msg":"佢搞得掂佢個購物平台先講野啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb481a574ac8aa3157649f201ddf2816e56d475c","tid":300941,"uid":12304,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T10:39:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b45b4544fd9c49d6511b59219c3b48f89c9386e3","tid":300941,"uid":31841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T10:44:40.000Z","msg":"條友政協黎架on9仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n係班港豬先幫佢打飛機"},{"pid":"48b11f8ce77dfea253d7b93602804d0087635e19","tid":300941,"uid":29314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T23:38:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>條友政協黎架on9仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n係班港豬先幫佢打飛機</blockquote><br />\n果陣有班高登仔瘋狂吹奏呢個生意佬"},{"pid":"dc013a6d532ffd161b0ea49e7b94c8470b0e3cab","tid":300941,"uid":59898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-01T00:28:46.000Z","msg":"<img